Interview-Friendly Definitions
Question	Answer
What is Confidentiality?	Protecting information from unauthorized access.
What is Integrity?	Ensuring data remains accurate, complete, and unmodified.
What is Availability?	Making sure systems and information are accessible when authorized users need them.
